{"type":"message","id":"622f1b82","parentId":"8bbaf760","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:18:20.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's now 5:18 AM. Still in the quiet window (23:00-08:00). I should check if there's an active task that needs continuation, and also check if there's work to do. Let me check the heartbeat and active task.\n\nI already read the HEARTBEAT.md in the previous heartbeat. It's the same content. The Active Task is still active. Current time is 5:18 AM - still in quiet hours.\n\nPer AGENTS.md: check MEMORY.md and memory files. But this is a heartbeat, not a full session start.\n\nPer HEARTBEAT.md rules:\n- 晚上 23:00-08:00 非紧急情况保持安静\n\n\n- 安静不等于停工，夜间应优先静默执行内部任务\n\nThe Active Task shows Status: active with T05 currently in progress, and the next steps involve running orders, probe guard, and control tower for the three profiles. Since it's still quiet hours and there's no emergency, I should continue executing the internal task of refactoring the three盘风格重构首轮代码. Let me check if the blueprint file exists.","thinkingSignature":"9758279059ab9c3c51458ac75dc9b5059fd49948301128e8be40668406cb0f68"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6xdqyjfv1vtz_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/t05_three_profile_style_refactor_round1_20260331.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":291,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":27917,"totalTokens":28282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774991891404,"responseId":"061b6d13b33e49785b00bb0aca25c49f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2666a28","parentId":"622f1b82","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:18:20.847Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6xdqyjfv1vtz_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# T05 三盘风格重构（首轮蓝图，20260331）\n\n## 触发原因\n\nT04 已确认当前低仓位属于规则层共振问题：三盘共享同一 runtime halt 与同一候选源，导致‘名义三盘、实际一盘共振’。\n\n## 首轮落实目标\n\n1. 风险真相改为**盘级**，不再让全局 `strategy_max_drawdown_pct(24.5100)` 同时封死三盘。\n2. 候选源改为**盘级风格**，至少把 aggressive / balanced / defensive 的 BUY 候选分层，而不是全盘复用同一套 merged_signals。\n3. 保留探测仓位，但把探测上限显式写成风格目标，避免三盘都塌到同一低仓位。\n\n## 首轮动作\n\n1. 把 aggressive / balanced / defensive 的 runtime 风险真相从共享 `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` 切为盘级风险真相，先解除‘一盘回撤、三盘全停’。\n2. 把三盘候选源从同一份 `merged_signals_20260330.csv` 拆层：aggressive 保留高弹性小盘，balanced 只保留中分以上且不过度追高的候选，defensive 仅保留最强 pass 候选或改走低波质量源。\n3. 把三盘探测预算写成明确风格台阶：aggressive 允许更高 probe 曝光，balanced 中档，defensive 最低，不再只是‘同一条规则略微改数字’。\n4. alpha55 单列处理：先修复选股/权重输出，使单日目标总权重不再长期卡在 6% 左右，再评估是否需要接入独立 probe guard。\n\n## 本轮可直接沿用的量化结论\n\n- aggressive：若仅去掉 shared runtime halt，按当前 AI 缩放 + 探测预算，新增曝光约 8.72%。\n- balanced：若仅去掉 shared runtime halt，按当前 AI 缩放 + 探测预算，新增曝光约 8.76%。\n- defensive：若仅去掉 shared runtime halt，按当前 AI 缩放 + 探测预算，新增曝光约 3.97%。\n- alpha55：当前不是 T05 三盘重构对象；它的主因是候选/权重本身过弱，需单独走 alpha55 选股权重修复。\n\n## 下一步最小实现件\n\n- 代码层：把三盘 runtime risk source 从全局 latest 切到盘级 risk truth/盘级 drawdown。\n- 配置层：三盘拆出不同 candidate source / ranking gate / probe budget。\n- 回归层：重新生成三盘 orders / probe_guard / control_tower，验证不再同跌同封。\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774991900840}}
{"type":"message","id":"51d0b8b0","parentId":"f2666a28","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:18:27.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The blueprint is clear. Now I need to execute T05. The current task is about the three盘 style refactor. The next items are:\n- Run orders/probe_guard/control_tower for aggressive/balanced/defensive\n- Split candidate source / ranking gate / probe budget\n- Fix alpha55's stock selection/weight output\n\nGiven it's 5:18 AM and in the quiet window, I should continue with the internal task of T05. This is a code execution task that can run silently.\n\nLet me start by:\n1. First checking the current runtime risk state to understand what needs to change\n2. Then implement the changes\n\nBut wait - let me check if there's been any git activity since the last commit. \n\nActually, I should just proceed with the implementation. Let me look at the current panel_profile_registry to see the three盘 setup, and run the scripts to re-generate things after making changes.","thinkingSignature":"c2d7a8f267e3a763e1c2dac2988e4f3b197e719c4b4138d13ae039c9cffac9c6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_63aiobf2tkql_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/panel_profile_registry.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3601,"output":239,"cacheRead":25232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29072,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774991900848,"responseId":"061b6d1d43ccdcd3192efa8a1d624b03"}}
{"type":"message","id":"748636e1","parentId":"51d0b8b0","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:18:27.680Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_63aiobf2tkql_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"from __future__ import annotations\n\nfrom typing import Any\n\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Panel-level runtime risk truth configuration\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 三盘重构核心：每盘使用独立的 runtime risk truth source，不再共享全局 halt。\n# 关键字段说明：\n#   strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct : 本盘允许的最大回撤阈值（触发 risk_off）\n#   strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct    : 本盘的硬停阈值（触发 halt_new_buy）\n#   halt_gate_source                   : 本盘的 halt gate 来源文件路径模板\n#   candidate_source_tag               : 本盘使用的候选股来源标签\n#   probe_budget_tag                   : 本盘使用的探测预算标签\n#\n# 当前全局风险真相（20260331）：strategy_max_drawdown_pct=24.51%，halt_new_buy=true\n# 三盘分层目标（首轮）：\n#   aggressive : strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct=30%, halt_pct=35%  （容忍最高回撤）\n#   balanced   : strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct=22%, halt_pct=28%\n#   defensive  : strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct=10%, halt_pct=15%  （与原全局一致）\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG: dict[str, dict[str, Any]] = {\n    \"aggressive\": {\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": 30.0,\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\": 35.0,\n        \"halt_gate_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_aggressive.json\",\n        \"candidate_source_tag\": \"aggressive_high_elasticity\",\n        \"probe_budget_tag\": \"probe_budget_high\",\n        \"risk_off_exposure_cap\": 0.85,\n        \"hard_stop_enabled\": True,\n    },\n    \"balanced\": {\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": 22.0,\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\": 28.0,\n        \"halt_gate_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_balanced.json\",\n        \"candidate_source_tag\": \"balanced_mid_quality\",\n        \"probe_budget_tag\": \"probe_budget_mid\",\n        \"risk_off_exposure_cap\": 0.70,\n        \"hard_stop_enabled\": True,\n    },\n    \"defensive\": {\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\": 10.0,\n        \"strategy_max_drawdown_halt_pct\": 15.0,\n        \"halt_gate_source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json\",\n        \"candidate_source_tag\": \"defensive_top_quality\",\n        \"probe_budget_tag\": \"probe_budget_low\",\n        \"risk_off_exposure_cap\": 0.55,\n        \"hard_stop_enabled\": True,\n    },\n}\n\n\ndef profile_runtime_risk_config(profile_slug: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Return the panel-level runtime risk config for a given profile slug.\n\n    Returns a copy so callers can mutate without affecting the registry.\n    Falls back to the defensive defaults if the slug is not found.\n    \"\"\"\n    default_cfg = PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG.get(\"defensive\", {})\n    return dict(PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG.get(profile_slug, default_cfg))\n\n\ndef is_panel_level_risk_enabled(profile_slug: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"Return True if this profile uses the new panel-level runtime risk truth.\"\"\"\n    return profile_slug in PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG\n\n\nCURRENT_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS: list[dict[str, Any]] = [\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"exit_dual\",\n        \"name\": \"双阈退出验证盘（paper_exit_dual）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"双阈退出验证盘\",\n        \"group\": \"exit_validation\",\n        \"group_label\": \"退出实验/失效盘\",\n    },\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"exit_tight\",\n        \"name\": \"紧阈退出验证盘（paper_exit_tight）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"紧阈退出验证盘\",\n        \"group\": \"exit_validation\",\n        \"group_label\": \"退出实验/失效盘\",\n    },\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"alpha55\",\n        \"name\": \"Alpha55 纸盘（paper_alpha55）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"Alpha55 纸盘\",\n        \"group\": \"current_paper\",\n        \"group_label\": \"当前有效纸盘\",\n    },\n]\n\nLEGACY_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS: list[dict[str, Any]] = [\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"defensive\",\n        \"name\": \"保守纸盘（paper_defensive）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"保守纸盘\",\n        \"group\": \"legacy_paper\",\n        \"group_label\": \"历史兼容纸盘\",\n    },\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"balanced\",\n        \"name\": \"均衡纸盘（paper_balanced）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"均衡纸盘\",\n        \"group\": \"legacy_paper\",\n        \"group_label\": \"历史兼容纸盘\",\n    },\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"aggressive\",\n        \"name\": \"进取纸盘（paper_aggressive）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"进取纸盘\",\n        \"group\": \"legacy_paper\",\n        \"group_label\": \"历史兼容纸盘\",\n    },\n]\n\nBREADTH_PROFILE_SPECS: list[dict[str, Any]] = [\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"breadth_strict_oos\",\n        \"name\": \"严格样本外宽度盘（breadth_strict_oos）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"严格样本外宽度盘\",\n        \"group\": \"breadth_experimental\",\n        \"group_label\": \"宽度实验盘\",\n    },\n    {\n        \"slug\": \"breadth_aggressive\",\n        \"name\": \"进取宽度独立盘（breadth_aggressive）\",\n        \"short_name\": \"进取宽度独立盘\",\n        \"group\": \"breadth_experimental\",\n        \"group_label\": \"宽度实验盘\",\n    },\n]\n\nPAPER_PROFILE_SPECS: list[dict[str, Any]] = CURRENT_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS + LEGACY_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS\nALL_STRATEGY_PROFILE_SPECS: list[dict[str, Any]] = PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS + BREADTH_PROFILE_SPECS\n\nCURRENT_PAPER_SLUGS = {item[\"slug\"] for item in CURRENT_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS}\nLEGACY_PAPER_SLUGS = {item[\"slug\"] for item in LEGACY_PAPER_PROFILE_SPECS}\nBREADTH_SLUGS = {item[\"slug\"] for item in BREADTH_PROFILE_SPECS}\n\nGROUP_ORDER = {\n    \"current_paper\": 0,\n    \"exit_validation\": 1,\n    \"breadth_experimental\": 2,\n    \"legacy_paper\": 3,\n}\n\n\ndef strategy_profile_spec(slug: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    for item in ALL_STRATEGY_PROFILE_SPECS:\n        if item[\"slug\"] == slug:\n            return item\n    return {\n        \"slug\": slug,\n        \"name\": slug,\n        \"short_name\": slug,\n        \"group\": \"unknown\",\n        \"group_label\": \"其他\",\n    }\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774991907672}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9524f2c","parentId":"748636e1","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:18:34.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. I can see that `panel_profile_registry.py` already has the `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG` defined with per-panel runtime risk configs. However, these config entries reference `runtime_risk_state_latest_aggressive.json`, `runtime_risk_state_latest_balanced.json`, `runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json` - but those files likely don't exist yet.\n\nNow I need to understand what T05 really needs:\n1. Generate per-panel runtime risk truth files\n2. The scripts that use runtime risk truth need to be updated to use per-panel files when generating orders/probe_guard for each profile\n\n\n3. Then re-run orders/probe_guard/control_tower for each of the three panels\n\nLet me check how the scripts currently consume the runtime risk config to see what needs to be modified.","thinkingSignature":"d1bc7cc01e513f1cfa914dc9fb81b6903874e24fcacebb884d9fff847c62b98b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e7s07e5lxz6e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/ | head -40"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e7s07e5lxz6e_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/runtime_risk_state_latest*.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"NO runtime_risk_state files found\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5389,"output":286,"cacheRead":25232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30907,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774991907680,"responseId":"061b6d236ab63505fa31b3266dd13e07"}}
