{"type":"message","id":"e5dfcc30","parentId":"e92e54b5","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:21:21.537Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue! The per-panel aggressive file has `base_runtime.halt_new_buy = false` and `base_runtime.risk_off = false`, but it also has a nested `base_runtime.runtime_truth` which overrides this. The `runtime_truth` section has `halt_new_buy: true` and `risk_off: true` and `buy_authorized: false`.\n\nThe `get_runtime_truth()` function from `runtime_state_schema.py` reads the `base_runtime.runtime_truth` section, not `base_runtime` directly. This means the `runtime_truth` section is computed from the OLD logic (using the global thresholds) and overrides the panel-specific thresholds I set.\n \nThe per-panel file was generated correctly with the right thresholds at the top level, but the `runtime_truth` section embedded within it was copied from the global file and still reflects the old threshold values. So when the schema function extracts the truth, it's pulling from that stale nested section instead of the fresh panel-specific one.\n\nI need to either update the schema function to use the per-panel threshold values from `PROFILE_RUNTIME_RISK_CONFIG` when computing `halt_new_buy` and `risk_off`, or I need to regenerate the per-panel files with the correct `runtime_truth` sections baked in. The real issue is that my generation script created the right thresholds but then pulled in the wrong pre-computed truth section from the global file. The nested `runtime_truth` inside `base_runtime` is overriding my panel-specific settings because it was copied from the global file. I need to regenerate the per-panel files so that `runtime_truth` reflects the per-panel halt thresholds instead.","thinkingSignature":"ac0af0ee5ba0ff56b309e0869c4fd7c61b8d6c9d8c33eb2783b9bc93a5e6718d"},{"type":"text","text":"I see the issue — the `runtime_truth` nested section in the per-panel file is still using global thresholds (copied from the global file). Let me fix the generation script:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8vn2y5qgyh1k_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"old_string":"    # Build the panel runtime risk state\n    panel_risk = {\n        **global_risk,\n        \"generated_at\": global_risk.get(\"generated_at\", \"\"),\n        \"panel\": profile_slug,\n        \"panel_halt_threshold_pct\": halt_pct,\n        \"panel_riskoff_threshold_pct\": riskoff_pct,\n        \"runtime_metrics\": {\n            **global_metrics,\n            \"panel_strategy_max_dd_pct\": current_dd,\n        },\n        \"base_runtime\": {\n            **(global_risk.get(\"base_runtime\") or {}),\n            \"mode\": \"cautious\" if risk_off else (\"normal\" if not halt_new_buy else \"halted\"),\n            \"halt_new_buy\": halt_new_buy,\n            \"risk_off\": risk_off,\n            \"halt_reason\": f\"strategy_max_drawdown_pct({current_dd:.4f}) >= {halt_pct:.4f}\" if halt_new_buy else \"\",\n            \"gate_reasons\": gate_reasons,\n        },\n        \"note\": f\"Per-panel runtime risk truth for {profile_slug}: halt>@{halt_pct}%(dd={current_dd}%), riskoff>@{riskoff_pct}%\",\n    }","newString":"    # Build the panel runtime risk state\n    # NOTE: The base_runtime section contains a nested runtime_truth (pre-computed\n    # from global thresholds) which overrides our panel-level fields when read\n    # by runtime_state_schema.get_runtime_truth(). We must also override that\n    # nested runtime_truth with the correct per-panel halt decision.\n    panel_risk = {\n        **global_risk,\n        \"generated_at\": global_risk.get(\"generated_at\", \"\"),\n        \"panel\": profile_slug,\n        \"panel_halt_threshold_pct\": halt_pct,\n        \"panel_riskoff_threshold_pct\": riskoff_pct,\n        \"runtime_metrics\": {\n            **global_metrics,\n            \"panel_strategy_max_dd_pct\": current_dd,\n        },\n        \"base_runtime\": {\n            **(global_risk.get(\"base_runtime\") or {}),\n            \"mode\": \"cautious\" if risk_off else (\"normal\" if not halt_new_buy else \"halted\"),\n            \"halt_new_buy\": halt_new_buy,\n            \"risk_off\": risk_off,\n            \"halt_reason\": f\"strategy_max_drawdown_pct({current_dd:.4f}) >= {halt_pct:.4f}\" if halt_new_buy else \"\",\n            \"gate_reasons\": gate_reasons,\n            # Override the nested runtime_truth with correct per-panel values\n            \"runtime_truth\": {\n                \"state\": \"risk_off\" if risk_off else (\"normal\" if not halt_new_buy else \"halted\"),\n                \"state_reason\": f\"strategy_max_drawdown_pct({current_dd:.4f}) >= {riskoff_pct:.4f}\" if risk_off else \"\",\n                \"trading_status\": \"BUY_HALT\" if halt_new_buy else \"TRADING\",\n                \"trading_status_reason\": f\"strategy_max_drawdown_pct({current_dd:.4f}) >= {halt_pct:.4f}\" if halt_new_buy else \"per_panel_ok\",\n                \"trading_status_label_cn\": \"禁止买入\" if halt_new_buy else \"正常交易\",\n                \"mode\": \"cautious\" if risk_off else (\"normal\" if not halt_new_buy else \"halted\"),\n                \"risk_off\": risk_off,\n                \"hard_stop\": False,\n                \"halt_new_buy\": halt_new_buy,\n                \"gate_reasons\": gate_reasons,\n                \"buy_authorized\": not halt_new_buy,\n                \"trading_ready\": not halt_new_buy,\n                \"severity\": \"RED\" if halt_new_buy else (\"YELLOW\" if risk_off else \"GREEN\"),\n                \"source\": f\"per_panel_t05_{profile_slug}\",\n                \"pipeline_ok\": True,\n                \"precheck_passed\": None,\n                \"advice_only\": True,\n            },\n        },\n        \"note\": f\"Per-panel runtime risk truth for {profile_slug}: halt>@{halt_pct}%(dd={current_dd}%), riskoff>@{riskoff_pct}%\",\n    }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19487,"o