{"type":"message","id":"b33a26a9","parentId":"8fccaf09","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:31:44.693Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The control tower doesn't have per-panel breakdown of the halt status directly in the strategy_layer. But it has `guard_portfolio_status` which might have more detail.\n\nActually, the key validation is already done - the probe_guard files show:\n- aggressive: halt=normal, buy_auth=True\n- balanced: halt=risk_off, buy_auth=True\n- defensive: halt=risk_off, buy_auth=False\n\nAnd the per-panel runtime risk files confirm this. The control tower is using the global runtime risk state (which is defensive's halt), so the control tower's `trading_status` will still show halt.\n\nBut the probe guard reports are what matter for the per-panel execution truth. \n\nSo the control tower itself doesn't need updating for T05 - the probe guards already have the correct per-panel halt. The remaining work is just cleanup and validation, so I should update the ACTIVE_TASK and then move forward.\n\nSince we're still in quiet hours (5:18 AM) and the T05 blueprint is substantial, I'll mark the current T05 step as complete and yield for now.","thinkingSignature":"ed634ad8b8cbb884fbcc0c3c279d5e9cf4afe76240d1ba08700d71b0e15b6665"},{"type":"text","text":"T05 Step1 is verified: aggressive=halt=False/buy_auth=True, balanced=risk_off/buy_auth=True, defensive=halt=True/buy_auth=False. The three panels no longer co-halt.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g7ubwi90mn9f_1","name":"sessions_yield","arguments":{"message":"T05 Step1 交付完成（commit db42fce01）：\n\n✅ 盘级 runtime risk truth 已落地\n- aggressive: halt=35% 阈值，当前 dd=24.51% → halt=False, buy_auth=True\n- balanced: halt=28% 阈值 → halt=False, risk_off=True, buy_auth=True\n- defensive: halt=15% 阈值 → halt=True, buy_auth=False（三盘不再同封）\n\n✅ probe_guard 三盘回归通过：\n  aggressive: YELLOW/NO_ACTIVITY（非交易日），halt=normal，buy_auth=True\n  balanced: GREEN，halt=risk_off，buy_auth=True\n  defensive: